  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located actually <strong>inside the Valley of the Temples</strong> archaeological park and with views of the nearby Temples of Concordia and Juno, this hotel is one of the best known in Sicily. Although starting life as a residence at the end of the 18th century, it has recently been renovated to create elegant and stylish spaces. The hotel’s outdoor pool is surrounded by gardens which blend into the surrounding landscape of almond and olive trees. The restaurant serves Sicilian cuisine with a modern twist, which can also be enjoyed on the Terrace of the Gods with views of the temples illuminated at night.</p>]]></description>
